snippet.title: Call of Duty Black Ops 6: Gameplay Reveal Trailer - Xbox Games Showcase 2024
snippet.description:
Forced to go rogue. Hunted from within. This is Call of Duty: Black Ops 6All-new campaign set in the Gulf War era 💥

12 new 6v6 maps & 4 new strike maps at launch 🗺️

Return of Round-based Zombies 🧟‍♂️  

Play it day one with Xbox Game Pass or Pre-order now: https://www.xbox.com/games/call-of-duty-black-ops-6
